reviewText: I have seen 16 of the Carry On movies, and Carry On Follow That Camel, which is on this DVD, is my favorite.
Very funny if you have English humour - and as I do it reminded me of the old days back home! I had not seen the feature with "Sergeant Bilko" so that was a plus!!
I first heard of the Carry On films when I was watching You Tube, and after a few weeks, I went onto Amazon and bought a copy of it; I found it to be incredibly funny and had alot of pizazz.
